Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Helsinki Accords
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z8jv0
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 13 Jul 1975
Helsinki Accords treaty - aimed at removing tension between Soviets and NATO countries - finally signed. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less